<p>
<lb n="1"/>śubhamastu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī jayābhyudaya śā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>livāhana śakavarṣaṁbulu 1660 A 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>gunēṭi kāḷayukti nāma saṁvvatsara mā 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kha(gha) śudha(ddha) 7 Ā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> bellamu koṁḍa śīmalō krō 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>sūrilō śrīvīrabhadrasvāmi caraṇāra 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>viṁdāla saṁnnidhini daṁtanāla tripurā 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁtakuni naptruḍunnu mallappapautṛ ḍuṁ 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>nu śaṁbhuliṁgaṁ putṛ ḍuṁnu Ayina 
<lb n="9"/>mallappa Anē bhaktuḍu jiṁhvapra 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>daṁ cēsukuni yiśvaruni cātame 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vaḍaśi padakoṁḍu dhinamulaku jiṁhva 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>yappa<unclear>bha</unclear>valenu molicivaccenu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="13"/>jātasya jāyamānasya garbha 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>sthasyāpidēhinaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> mābhū 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>nmamakulē janmayasyaśaṁ 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>bhurnnadaivataṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī śrī śrī śrī śrī <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

